{"source":{"uri":"Features/UserJourney.feature","data":"Feature: Complete User Journey on EHU Website\r\n  As a visitor\r\n  I want to navigate the website, switch languages, search for information, and view contact details\r\n  So that I can verify the website works correctly end-to-end\r\n\r\n  @smoke @e2e\r\n  Scenario: User completes a full journey through the EHU website\r\n    Given I open the home page\r\n    When I switch the language to \"Lithuanian\"\r\n    Then the URL should contain \"lt.ehuniversity.lt\"\r\n\r\n    When I navigate to \"About\"\r\n    Then the page title should contain \"About\"\r\n\r\n    When I search for \"Rector\"\r\n    Then the URL should contain \"?s=Rector\"\r\n\r\n    When I open the contact page\r\n    Then I should see at least 4 contact items\r\n    And the email should be \"franciskscarynacr@gmail.com\"\r\n    And the Lithuanian phone should be \"+370 68 771365\"\r\n    And the Belarusian phone should be \"+375 29 5781488\"\r\n    And the social block should contain \"Facebook\"\r\n    And the social block should contain \"Telegram\"\r\n    And the social block should contain \"VK\"\r\n","mediaType":"text/x.cucumber.gherkin+plain"}}
